  "What is the quadratic formula?": "二次公式是什么?",
  "x = (b +/- sqrt(b^2 - 4ac)) / (2a)": "x = (b + /- sqrt (b2 - 4ac) / (2a)",
  "x = (-b +/- sqrt(b^2 - 4ac)) / (2a)": "x = (-b + /- sqrt (b2 - 4ac)) / (2(a))",
  "x = (-b +/- sqrt(b^2 + 4ac)) / (2a)": "x = (-b +/- sqrt (b2 + 4ac)) / (2(a))",
  "x = -b / (2a)": "x = -b / (2a)",
  "The quadratic formula x = (-b +/- sqrt(b^2 - 4ac)) / (2a) gives the solutions to any quadratic equation ax^2 + bx + c = 0 when a is not zero.": "二次方程式 x = (-b +/- sqrt (b2 - 4ac)) / (2a) 为任何二次方程式ax2 + bx + c = 0 当一不是零时提供答案。",
  "What is the discriminant of a quadratic equation?": "二次方程的分歧是什么?",
  "The sum of the roots, particularly regarding real": "根源的总和,特别是真正的",
  "The coefficient of x^2 following conventional understanding": "常规理解后x%2的系数",
  "The value -b/(2a), particularly regarding repeated in": "-b/(2a) 值,特别是",
  "The expression b^2 - 4ac that determines the nature of the solutions": "b2 - 4ac 确定解决方案性质的表达式",
  "The discriminant D = b^2 - 4ac is the expression under the square root in the quadratic formula. Its value determines whether the solutions are real or complex, and distinct or repeated.": "d = b2 - 4ac 是二次公式中方根下的表达式。 它的价值决定解决方案是真实的还是复杂的, 并且是不同的还是重复的 。",
  "What does a positive discriminant indicate?": "积极对立者表示什么?",
  "The parabola has no vertex": "抛物线没有顶部",
  "When b^2 - 4ac > 0, the square root yields a real positive number, and the +/- produces two different values. This means the quadratic has two distinct real roots.": "当 b2 - 4ac > 0 时, 平方根产生实际正数, + / 产生两个不同的值。 这意味着四方形有两个不同的实际根。",
  "What does a zero discriminant indicate?": "零歧见意味着什么?",
  "The equation is not quadratic": "方程不是二次方程",
  "Exactly one repeated real solution (a double root)": "完全重复一个真正的解决方案(双根)",
  "When b^2 - 4ac = 0, the square root is zero, and x = -b/(2a) is the only solution. Graphically, the parabola touches the x-axis at exactly one point (the vertex).": "当 b2 - 4ac = 0时, 平方根为零, x = -b/ (2a) 是唯一的溶液。 从图形上看, 抛物线在完全一个点( 顶点) 触及 x 轴 。",
  "What does a negative discriminant indicate?": "负面的对立者表示什么?",
  "Two negative real solutions": "两个消极的实际解决办法",
  "Two complex conjugate solutions (no real solutions)": "两个复杂的共同解决办法(没有真正的解决办法)",
  "The equation cannot be solved": "方程式无法解答",
  "One repeated solution": "一个反复重复的解决方案",
  "When b^2 - 4ac < 0, the square root of a negative number produces imaginary values. The two solutions are complex conjugates, and the parabola does not cross the x-axis.": "当 b2 - 4ac < 0 时, 负数的平根产生假想值。 两种解决方案是复杂的共产物, 而抛物线没有跨过 X 轴 。",
  "What are complex conjugate roots?": "什么是复杂的共生根源?",
  "Roots that add up to zero": "加起来为零的根根根",
  "A pair of complex numbers of the form a + bi and a - bi": "+ 双和- 双的窗体的复数",
  "Roots that are both negative": "两者均为负的根根",
  "Roots that are reciprocals of each other": "彼此对等的根",
  "Complex conjugate roots come in pairs: a + bi and a - bi, where i = sqrt(-1). They always occur together when a quadratic with real coefficients has a negative discriminant.": "复杂的同源根是成对的:一对加二对和一对二对,其中i = sqrt(-1) 。 当具有实际系数的二次方块出现负差异时,它们总是同时出现。",
  "What does 'rational root' mean?": "\"合理根\"是什么意思?",
  "A root that is positive": "一个积极的根根",
  "A root that is always a whole number": "永远是一个整数的根根",
  "A root that can be expressed as a fraction p/q where p and q are integers": "根,可以用分数 p/q 表示,p和q是整数",
  "A root that involves square roots": "涉及平根的根根",
  "A rational root is a solution that can be written as a ratio of two integers. When the discriminant is a perfect square, the quadratic formula produces rational roots.": "理性根是一个可以写成两个整数之比的解决方案。 当对立方是完美的正方形时, 二次公式产生合理的根。",
  "What does 'irrational root' mean?": "什么是\"理性根\"是什么意思?",
  "A root involving the imaginary unit i": "涉及想象单位i的根",
  "A root that is undefined": "未定义的根根根",
  "A root that is negative": "阴性的根根",
  "A root that cannot be expressed as a simple fraction": "不能以简单分数表示的根根",
  "An irrational root is a real number that cannot be expressed as a ratio of integers. This occurs when the discriminant is positive but not a perfect square, such as sqrt(5).": "非理性根是一个无法以整数比表示的真实数字。 当对立面是正数而不是完美的正方形时, 就会出现这种情况, 比如 sqrt(5) 。",
  "What is the 'plus or minus' symbol (+/-) in the quadratic formula?": "二次公式中的“ 增减” 符号 (+/-) 是什么 ?",
  "It means the formula has an error": "表示公式有错误",
  "It indicates that both addition and subtraction should be used to find the two solutions": "它指出,增加和减减应同时用来找到两种解决办法",
  "It indicates multiplication": "表示乘数",
  "It means the answer can be positive or negative": "这意味着答案可以是正面的,也可以是否定的",
  "The +/- symbol means you compute two separate values: one using addition (-b + sqrt(D))/(2a) and one using subtraction (-b - sqrt(D))/(2a). These give the two solutions of the quadratic.": "+/- 符号表示您计算两个独立的值: 一个使用添加值 (-b + sqrt(D)) / (2a) , 一个使用减法 (-b - sqrt(D) ) / (2a) 。 这给出了二次方形的两个解决方案 。",
  "What does the term 'double root' mean?": "“双根”一词是什么意思?",
  "A root that is twice as large as expected": "根的面积是预期的两倍",
  "Two different positive roots": "两种不同的积极根源",
  "A root of a degree-2 polynomial only": "仅一度 - 2 多圆性根根根",
  "A root that appears twice because the discriminant is zero": "根的出现两次,因为对立是零",
  "A double root (or repeated root) occurs when the discriminant equals zero, meaning the quadratic formula gives only one value. The parabola touches the x-axis at exactly that point.": "当对角值为零时会出现双根(或重复根),这意味着二次公式只给出一个值。在那个点,抛物线会触碰 x 轴。",
  "A model rocket's height is h(t) = -16t^2 + 96t. Using the quadratic formula, find when the rocket hits the ground.": "型号火箭的高度是h(t) = -16t2 + 96t。使用二次方程式,当火箭击中地面时会发现。",
